sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant API
  participant Policy
  participant Retrieval
  participant Graph
  participant Vector
  participant Rules
  participant LLM
  participant Audit
  participant Workflow

  User->>API: Ask why anomaly happened
  API->>Policy: Validate tenant, role, data scope
  Policy-->>API: Allowed scope
  API->>Retrieval: Build evidence context
  Retrieval->>Graph: Traverse dependencies and impacts
  Retrieval->>Vector: Search documents/tickets
  Retrieval->>Rules: Load domain rules and thresholds
  Retrieval-->>API: Evidence pack
  API->>LLM: Synthesize with bounded context
  LLM-->>API: Explanation draft
  API->>Policy: Claim/evidence/action validation
  API->>Audit: Store question, evidence, answer, policy
  API-->>User: Causes, confidence, evidence, next actions
  User->>Workflow: Approve action if needed
  Workflow->>Audit: Store approval and execution trace
